Code based on the following repos.

https://github.com/Akkiesoft/akkiesoft-pico/tree/main/MicroPython/test-pico-pcd8544
https://github.com/kfricke/micropython-nunchuck


Connections
Nokia
Gnd: Pico GND (38)
BL : Pico GP28(34)
Vcc: Pico 3V3 (36)
Clk: Pico GP6 ( 9)
Din: Pico GP7 (10)
DC : Pico GP4 ( 6)
CE : Pico GP5 ( 7)
RST: Pico GP8 (11)

Wii Nunchuk
SCL - GPIO 17 (22)
SDK - GPIO 16 (21)
